334
01:07:42,600 --> 01:07:44,170
how to survive,

335
01:07:44,920 --> 01:07:46,570
and how to live off the land

336
01:07:53,320 --> 01:07:55,209
But he was a tormented soul

337
01:07:55,440 --> 01:07:57,249
Haunted by his demons,

338
01:07:57,400 --> 01:07:59,721
he couldn't take care of me

339
01:08:03,960 --> 01:08:07,123
So he sent me on an old fishing boat,
to a distant land

340
01:08:07,240 --> 01:08:09,607
to find a person he thought could

341
