358
01:09:32,200 --> 01:09:33,440
It's okay, cry

359
01:09:35,640 --> 01:09:38,086
Shiro, I'll be back as soon as possible

360
01:09:40,880 --> 01:09:42,041
I love you

361
01:09:56,960 --> 01:09:59,088
Of all the assassins on my hit list,

362
01:09:59,280 --> 01:10:01,567
Ken is the one that I'm most worried of

363
01:10:02,040 --> 01:10:05,169
