that no place is safe for him

370
01:10:23,800 --> 01:10:25,848
Not even his own backyard

371
01:10:50,640 --> 01:10:54,201
Sam, you managed to kill my whole team

372
01:10:54,560 --> 01:10:56,164
I'm impressed

373
01:10:56,480 --> 01:10:57,970
