374
01:11:08,160 --> 01:11:09,571
You know you won't leave here alive

375
01:11:46,520 --> 01:11:48,284
So what do you think Sam?

376
01:11:48,440 --> 01:11:51,364
Maybe I'll just cut off your limbs

377
01:11:51,640 --> 01:11:54,325
So you can spend the rest of your days

378
01:11:54,880 --> 01:11:56,370
in guilt

379
01:11:56,600 --> 01:11:58,762
It's you who caused

380
01:12:00,760 --> 01:12:02,649
